<p>{% include linkrefs.html %}</p>

<h1 id="overview">Overview</h1>

<p>The Reference API allows you to easily access a list of supported Countries, States, TimeZones and Currencies.</p>

<h1 id="endpoints">Endpoints</h1>

<ul>
<li>Sandbox: <a href="https://referencedemo.iqmetrix.net/v1">https://referencedemo.iqmetrix.net/v1</a></li>
<li>Production: <a href="https://reference.iqmetrix.net/v1">https://reference.iqmetrix.net/v1</a></li>
</ul>

<h1 id="resources">Resources</h1>

<h2 id="country">Country</h2>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align: left">Name</th>
<th style="text-align: left">Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left">Id (<code class="prettyprint">Integer</code>)</td>
<td style="text-align: left">Identifier</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left">Code (<code class="prettyprint">String</code>)</td>
<td style="text-align: left">Country Code. Uses the ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 standard</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left">Name (<code class="prettyprint">String</code>)</td>
<td style="text-align: left">Country name</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left">Version (<code class="prettyprint">Integer</code>)</td>
<td style="text-align: left">Latest version number</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left">States (<code class="prettyprint">Array[&lt;a href=&#39;/api/reference/#state&#39;&gt;State&lt;/a&gt;]</code>)</td>
<td style="text-align: left">States/Provinces</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left"><em>Alpha3Code (<code class="prettyprint">String</code>)</em></td>
<td style="text-align: left"><em>Reserved for future use</em></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

